### Playlist Service — HTTP Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8083
### Start service: pnpm nx run playlist-service:serve (requires Docker infra)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8083

# Paste the accessToken returned from user-service login here
@accessToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9...
@authToken = Bearer {{accessToken}}

# Paste second user's token here (for collaborator tests)
@accessToken2 = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9...
@authToken2 = Bearer {{accessToken2}}

# Fill in after creating a playlist
@playlistId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

# Fill in after adding a track (item id from addTrack response)
@itemId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002

# A valid trackId from catalog-service
@trackId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003

# A valid trackId2 from catalog-service (for second track)
@trackId2 = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000004

# Another user's ID (for collaborator tests)
@collaboratorUserId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005

# Owner user ID (fill in from login)
@myUserId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000006


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PLAYLISTS — CRUD
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [1] Create private playlist — 201 Created
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "My Chill Mix",
  "description": "Weekend vibes playlist",
  "visibility": "PRIVATE"
}

###

### [2] Create public playlist — 201 Created
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Top Hits 2025",
  "description": "Popular tracks this year",
  "visibility": "PUBLIC"
}

###

### [3] Create unlisted playlist — 201 Created
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Secret Playlist",
  "visibility": "UNLISTED"
}

###

### [4] Create playlist — name too long (>100 chars) → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "This name is way too long and exceeds the one hundred character limit set by the validation constraint here",
  "visibility": "PUBLIC"
}

###

### [5] Create playlist — missing name → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "description": "No name provided",
  "visibility": "PUBLIC"
}

###

### [6] Create playlist — no token → 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Unauthorized Playlist",
  "visibility": "PUBLIC"
}

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PLAYLISTS — LIST MY PLAYLISTS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [7] GET my playlists (owned + collaborating) — default page
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### [8] GET my playlists — page 2, size 5
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists?page=1&size=5
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### [9] GET my playlists — no token → 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PLAYLISTS — GET BY ID
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [10] GET playlist by id — owner (full detail, isOwner=true, canEdit=true)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### [11] GET public playlist — no auth (isOwner=false, canEdit=false)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}

###

### [12] GET private playlist — other user → 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}
Authorization: {{authToken2}}

###

### [13] GET non-existent playlist → 404
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PLAYLISTS — UPDATE
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [14] PATCH update name and description
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Updated Playlist Name",
  "description": "New description"
}

###

### [15] PATCH update visibility to PUBLIC (triggers PlaylistSharedEvent in outbox)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "visibility": "PUBLIC"
}

###

### [16] PATCH update visibility back to PRIVATE
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "visibility": "PRIVATE"
}

###

### [17] PATCH update name only
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Renamed Playlist"
}

###

### [18] PATCH — name too long → 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "This name is way too long and exceeds the one hundred character limit set by the validation constraint here"
}

###

### [19] PATCH — not owner → 403
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken2}}

{
  "name": "Stolen Name"
}

###

### [20] PATCH — no token → 401
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "No Auth Update"
}

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PLAYLISTS — DELETE
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [21] DELETE playlist — owner → 204
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### [22] DELETE playlist — not owner → 403
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}
Authorization: {{authToken2}}

###

### [23] DELETE non-existent playlist → 404
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### [24] DELETE playlist — no token → 401
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PLAYLIST ITEMS — ADD TRACK
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [25] POST add track — append to end (no position) → 201
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "trackId": "{{trackId}}"
}

###

### [26] POST add track — insert at position 1 → 201 (shifts others down)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "trackId": "{{trackId2}}",
  "position": 1
}

###

### [27] POST add duplicate track → 409 (already in playlist)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "trackId": "{{trackId}}"
}

###

### [28] POST add track — missing trackId → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "position": 1
}

###

### [29] POST add track — non-existent track → 404 (from catalog-service)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "trackId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

###

### [30] POST add track — collaborator (EDITOR role) → 201
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken2}}

{
  "trackId": "{{trackId}}"
}

###

### [31] POST add track — no token → 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackId": "{{trackId}}"
}

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PLAYLIST ITEMS — REMOVE TRACK
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [32] DELETE remove track from playlist → 204
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}/items/{{itemId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### [33] DELETE remove track — not editor → 403
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}/items/{{itemId}}
Authorization: {{authToken2}}

###

### [34] DELETE remove track — wrong playlistId (item exists but different playlist) → 404
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/items/{{itemId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### [35] DELETE remove track — non-existent itemId → 404
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}/items/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### [36] DELETE remove track — no token → 401
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}/items/{{itemId}}

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PLAYLIST ITEMS — REORDER
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [37] PUT reorder items — full ordered list of itemIds → 204
### itemIds must contain exactly the current items in new desired order
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}/items/reorder
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "itemIds": [
    "{{itemId}}",
    "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002"
  ]
}

###

### [38] PUT reorder — missing an item (incomplete list) → 400
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}/items/reorder
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "itemIds": [
    "{{itemId}}"
  ]
}

###

### [39] PUT reorder — extra item not in playlist → 400
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}/items/reorder
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "itemIds": [
    "{{itemId}}",
    "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000099"
  ]
}

###

### [40] PUT reorder — not editor → 403
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}/items/reorder
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken2}}

{
  "itemIds": [
    "{{itemId}}"
  ]
}

###

### [41] PUT reorder — no token → 401
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}/items/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemIds": [
    "{{itemId}}"
  ]
}

###


