# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# COLLABORATORS — REMOVE
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [53] DELETE remove collaborator — owner removes someone → 204
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}/collaborators/{{collaboratorUserId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### [54] DELETE remove collaborator — self-remove → 204
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}/collaborators/{{collaboratorUserId}}
Authorization: {{authToken2}}

###

### [55] DELETE remove collaborator — not owner, removing someone else → 403
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}/collaborators/{{myUserId}}
Authorization: {{authToken2}}

###

### [56] DELETE remove collaborator — non-existent → 404
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}/collaborators/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### [57] DELETE remove collaborator — no token → 401
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/playlists/{{playlistId}}/collaborators/{{collaboratorUserId}}

###


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# USER PUBLIC PLAYLISTS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [58] GET public playlists of a user — no auth → 200 (PUBLIC only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{myUserId}}/playlists

###

### [59] GET public playlists — with auth → 200 (still PUBLIC only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{myUserId}}/playlists
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### [60] GET public playlists — paginated
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{myUserId}}/playlists?page=0&size=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### [61] GET public playlists — user with no public playlists → 200 empty page
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000099/playlists

###


